Get a serious bump in processing performance while plotting high-volume data such as ArcGIS Online layers and complex shape layers when you enable the new Salesforce Maps framework. Plan for and centralize your company’s unique segmentation, territories, and quota targets in Sales Planning. Determine compensation for reps based on their effective territory assignment dates in Enterprise Territory Management, now named Sales Territories.

Salesforce Maps and Salesforce Maps Advanced
Plot high-volume data such as ArcGIS Online layers and complex shape layers in a fraction of the usual time when you try out the new Salesforce Maps framework.

Sales Planning
Define a sales strategy with input from key stakeholders. Structure sales plans that reflect your company’s unique segmentation, territories, and quota targets—all in one place.

Sales Territories (Formerly Enterprise Territory Management)
Determine compensation for reps when their effective start and end dates differ from the dates they were added to and removed from their assigned territories.
